<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>以色列新闻RSS</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Sun, 16 Jun 2024 16:07:55 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>和平企业家毛兹·伊农 (Maoz Inon) 在拿撒勒这座“希望悬崖上的城市”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-16/ty-article-magazine/.premium/in-nazareth-city-on-the-precipice-of-hope-with-peace-entrepreneur-maoz-inon/00000190-20a8-d3e6-a191-76abb5d40000</link><description>2020 年，随着 COVID-19 大流行的肆虐，伊农开始了他的拿撒勒之旅。现在，10 月 7 日他的父母在以色列南部被哈马斯杀害后，他向参与者讲述了“创造希望”的行为以及旅游业作为共存力量的故事</description><pubDate>Sun, 16 Jun 2024 13:49:07 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-16/ty-article-magazine/.premium/in-nazareth-city-on-the-precipice-of-hope-with-peace-entrepreneur-maoz-inon/00000190-20a8-d3e6-a191-76abb5d40000</guid></item><item><title>以色列最高法院叫停国家审计长对以色列国防军辛贝特 10 月 7 日失败的调查</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-16/ty-article/.premium/israels-top-court-halts-state-comptrollers-probe-into-idf-shin-bet-oct-7-failures/00000190-2103-d3e6-a191-772b73890000</link><description>吉拉·坎菲·斯坦尼茨法官以“复杂的安全局势”为由解释了法院的决定，并补充说，推迟调查的决定也是根据国防官员向法院提交的机密声明而做出的。</description><pubDate>Sun, 16 Jun 2024 13:42:31 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-16/ty-article/.premium/israels-top-court-halts-state-comptrollers-probe-into-idf-shin-bet-oct-7-failures/00000190-2103-d3e6-a191-772b73890000</guid></item><item><title>以色列军队宣布每日“战术暂停”加沙战斗，以允许援助物资进入</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-16/ty-article/.premium/israeli-army-announces-daily-tactical-pause-in-gaza-fighting-to-allow-for-entry-of-aid/00000190-20cb-df6a-a3f6-2fdbe7120000</link><description>尽管内塔尼亚胡总理办公室否认总理了解这一政策，但军方官员表示，这符合他的命令。与国防部长加兰特关系密切的消息人士称，他并不了解军队的决定</description><pubDate>Sun, 16 Jun 2024 12:56:44 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-16/ty-article/.premium/israeli-army-announces-daily-tactical-pause-in-gaza-fighting-to-allow-for-entry-of-aid/00000190-20cb-df6a-a3f6-2fdbe7120000</guid></item><item><title>“课堂内外的以色列和巴勒斯坦话语有多么不同，令人震惊”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/podcasts/2024-06-16/ty-article-podcast/its-striking-how-different-israel-palestine-discourse-is-in-the-classroom-and-out-of-it/00000190-1204-d667-abf0-76cf342b0000</link><description></description><pubDate>Sun, 16 Jun 2024 12:49:05 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/podcasts/2024-06-16/ty-article-podcast/its-striking-how-different-israel-palestine-discourse-is-in-the-classroom-and-out-of-it/00000190-1204-d667-abf0-76cf342b0000</guid></item><item><title>巴勒斯坦人对哈马斯 10 月 7 日袭击的支持表明了他们与以色列人的共同点：绝望</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-16/ty-article/.premium/palestinian-support-for-hamas-oct-7-attack-shows-what-they-share-with-israelis-despair/00000190-2075-d880-a7f5-b4f58bcf0000</link><description>一项针对加沙和西岸巴勒斯坦人的最新民意调查显示，八个月的流血和破坏并没有削弱人们对哈马斯及其 10 月 7 日袭击的支持。对于以色列人、巴勒斯坦人和国际社会来说，其结果表明为什么冲突的新解决方案如此迫切</description><pubDate>Sun, 16 Jun 2024 11:54:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-16/ty-article/.premium/palestinian-support-for-hamas-oct-7-attack-shows-what-they-share-with-israelis-despair/00000190-2075-d880-a7f5-b4f58bcf0000</guid></item><item><title>哥伦比亚大学特别工作组揭露了自 10 月 7 日以来校园内学生和教职人员普遍存在的反犹太主义行为</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-06-16/ty-article-magazine/.premium/columbia-task-force-reveals-full-extent-of-antisemitism-on-campus-since-oct-7/00000190-205f-d880-a7f5-b4df117d0000</link><description>教授的反犹太主义言论、对犹太学生的骚扰——哥伦比亚大学反犹太主义特别工作组自 11 月成立以来已听取了数百份证词。其成员向《国土报》讲述了他们计划的强制方向，并表示他们已经就反犹太主义的“教育”定义达成一致。</description><pubDate>Sun, 16 Jun 2024 11:15:43 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-06-16/ty-article-magazine/.premium/columbia-task-force-reveals-full-extent-of-antisemitism-on-campus-since-oct-7/00000190-205f-d880-a7f5-b4df117d0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列新闻自由遭到破坏的历史性一天</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-16/ty-article/.premium/a-historic-day-in-the-destruction-of-israels-free-press/00000190-2067-df11-a3b9-a1671a220000</link><description>亿万富翁 Len Blavatnik 决定任命 Yulia Shamalov-Berkovich 为第 13 频道新闻首席执行官，标志着该频道作为强硬新闻机构的精神的终结。内塔尼亚胡还有另一个微笑的理由</description><pubDate>Sun, 16 Jun 2024 10:53:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-16/ty-article/.premium/a-historic-day-in-the-destruction-of-israels-free-press/00000190-2067-df11-a3b9-a1671a220000</guid></item><item><title>法国军火博览会组织者对禁止以色列国民参加活动的裁决提出上诉</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-16/ty-article/.premium/french-arms-expo-organizers-appeal-ruling-banning-israeli-nationals-from-event/00000190-2024-d3e6-a191-762f1ef40000</link><description>组织者表示，法院的裁决曲解了他们的意图，全面禁止以色列参加展览。消息人士称，这一决定遭到了以色列国防部长的严厉回应，法国国防部认为这一决定是不可接受的</description><pubDate>Sun, 16 Jun 2024 09:32:17 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-16/ty-article/.premium/french-arms-expo-organizers-appeal-ruling-banning-israeli-nationals-from-event/00000190-2024-d3e6-a191-762f1ef40000</guid></item><item><title>以色列国防军公布了周六拉法爆炸事件中六名士兵的名字，以及加沙北部两名士兵的名字</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-16/ty-article/.premium/idf-names-five-soldiers-killed-in-saturdays-rafah-blast-and-two-killed-in-northern-gaza/00000190-1fd3-d4b4-a7d6-dff30cc60000</link><description>军方周六公布了在加沙地带战斗中阵亡的10名士兵的姓名，其中包括一名自愿参加预备役的49岁祖父和一名19岁的战斗工程兵</description><pubDate>Sun, 16 Jun 2024 08:26:40 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-16/ty-article/.premium/idf-names-five-soldiers-killed-in-saturdays-rafah-blast-and-two-killed-in-northern-gaza/00000190-1fd3-d4b4-a7d6-dff30cc60000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡和以色列国防军高层就加沙停火展开斗争，同时与真主党展开全面战争</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-16/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-idf-top-brass-fight-over-gaza-truce-while-spiraling-towards-war-with-hezbollah/00000190-1d17-d231-a1b2-fd5fbd450000</link><description>周六八名以色列国防军士兵的死亡表明，面对哈马斯的适应性策略是困难的，哈马斯将其转变为松散的游击队组织 ■ 内塔尼亚胡继续推销“全面胜利”，再次委托其他人传递坏消息</description><pubDate>Sun, 16 Jun 2024 03:01:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-16/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-idf-top-brass-fight-over-gaza-truce-while-spiraling-towards-war-with-hezbollah/00000190-1d17-d231-a1b2-fd5fbd450000</guid></item><item><title>以色列国防军在以色列北部纳哈里亚海滩附近击落可疑空中目标</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-16/ty-article-live/eight-idf-soldiers-killed-in-rafah-blast-idf-soldier-dies-from-combat-wounds-in-gaza/00000190-1ea9-d880-a7f5-befd4ae80000</link><description>以色列军队宣布每天上午 8 点至晚上 7 点之间进行“战术暂停”，试图增加向加沙提供的援助。 ■ 两名预备役军人在加沙北部的坦克爆炸中身亡；以色列国防军公布了在拉法装甲运兵车爆炸中丧生的 6 名士兵的姓名 ■ 反对政府的抗议者封锁了以色列各地的主要高速公路 ■ 以色列国防军：袭击了黎巴嫩南部的真主党目标 ■ 美国海军部队从红海被胡塞武装袭击的希腊船只上营救船员</description><pubDate>Sun, 16 Jun 2024 02:36:48 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-16/ty-article-live/eight-idf-soldiers-killed-in-rafah-blast-idf-soldier-dies-from-combat-wounds-in-gaza/00000190-1ea9-d880-a7f5-befd4ae80000</guid></item><item><title>以色列国防军宣布，一名以色列士兵周一在拉法受伤身亡</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-16/ty-article/israeli-soldier-dies-from-wounds-sustained-in-rafah-on-monday-idf-announces/00000190-1da3-df11-a3b9-bda7264e0000</link><description>吉瓦蒂旅 19 岁的亚伊尔·罗特曼 (Yair Roitman) 中士在位于拉法东部沙布拉 (Shabura) 街区的一名哈马斯特工的房屋发生爆炸后受伤，该房屋内设了诱杀装置。罗特曼留下了他的父母和五个兄弟姐妹</description><pubDate>Sun, 16 Jun 2024 01:22:12 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-16/ty-article/israeli-soldier-dies-from-wounds-sustained-in-rafah-on-monday-idf-announces/00000190-1da3-df11-a3b9-bda7264e0000</guid></item><item><title>八名以色列士兵在拉法爆炸中丧生；以色列国防军士兵因早些时候在加沙的战斗受伤而死亡</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-15/ty-article-live/g7-leaders-express-concern-about-consequences-of-israels-ongoing-operation-in-rafah/00000190-1988-df11-a3b9-b98f9a730000</link><description>来自黎巴嫩的无人机在以色列北部坠毁，引发大火 ■ 军方表示，火箭袭击了以色列北部的以色列国防军基地附近，但没有造成任何损失的报告 ■ 报告：美国担心以色列对黎巴嫩的袭击正在为以色列国防军“为全面进攻做准备” 白宫国家安全顾问预计未来几天与哈马斯的停火谈判进展“缓慢” 以色列国防部长将访问五角大楼</description><pubDate>Sat, 15 Jun 2024 20:28:40 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-15/ty-article-live/g7-leaders-express-concern-about-consequences-of-israels-ongoing-operation-in-rafah/00000190-1988-df11-a3b9-b98f9a730000</guid></item><item><title>以色列战争第 253 天：以色列军队称加沙南部爆炸造成 8 名士兵死亡</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-15/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-253-israeli-army-says-eight-soldiers-killed-by-blast-in-south-gaza/00000190-1ce1-d3e6-a191-5eeb9d990000</link><description>八名以色列国防军士兵在拉法附近丧生 ■ 来自黎巴嫩的火箭弹落在以色列北部的以色列国防军基地附近，没有人员伤亡或财产损失 ■ 来自黎巴嫩的无人机坠落在西加利利，引发火灾 ■ 哥伦比亚广播公司新闻报道，一些美国官员认为以色列正在“准备对黎巴嫩更深处的打击”全面进攻的战场” ■ 战争进入 253 天后，您需要了解以下内容</description><pubDate>Sat, 15 Jun 2024 17:25:33 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-15/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-253-israeli-army-says-eight-soldiers-killed-by-blast-in-south-gaza/00000190-1ce1-d3e6-a191-5eeb9d990000</guid></item><item><title>数万以色列人抗议内塔尼亚胡联盟，呼吁达成加沙协议</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-15/ty-article/.premium/end-the-war-free-the-hostages-israelis-protest-netanyahu-coalition-call-for-gaza-deal/00000190-1c83-df11-a3b9-bd877d3e0000</link><description>代表加沙人质家属的一个组织发表声明说，“战争每多一天，以色列的利益就会受到损害”，这一点已经非常清楚了。警方发言人称，特拉维夫反政府抗议活动中有 12 人被捕</description><pubDate>Sat, 15 Jun 2024 16:37:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-15/ty-article/.premium/end-the-war-free-the-hostages-israelis-protest-netanyahu-coalition-call-for-gaza-deal/00000190-1c83-df11-a3b9-bd877d3e0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列国防军证实，八名以色列士兵在加沙南部拉法爆炸中丧生</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-15/ty-article/eight-israeli-soldiers-killed-by-blast-in-south-gazas-rafah-idf-announces/00000190-1caa-d4b4-a7d6-dcfa04f30000</link><description>以色列国防军发言人丹尼尔·哈加里（Daniel Hagari）表示，装甲运兵车的爆炸可能是由于航母附近放置的爆炸装置或向航母发射的反坦克导弹引起的。</description><pubDate>Sat, 15 Jun 2024 16:13:19 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-15/ty-article/eight-israeli-soldiers-killed-by-blast-in-south-gazas-rafah-idf-announces/00000190-1caa-d4b4-a7d6-dcfa04f30000</guid></item><item><title>“10月7日之后，中国的反犹太主义达到了最令人震惊的程度”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-15/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/after-october-7-antisemitism-in-china-reached-the-most-shocking-levels/00000190-19da-dee3-af9b-dfdb33a00000</link><description>中国文化专家尤瓦尔·温雷布 (Yuval Weinreb) 解释了社交媒体在中国的运作方式以及哈马斯袭击后网上发生的情况</description><pubDate>Sat, 15 Jun 2024 04:20:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-15/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/after-october-7-antisemitism-in-china-reached-the-most-shocking-levels/00000190-19da-dee3-af9b-dfdb33a00000</guid></item><item><title>特拉维夫的一个郊区屈服于东正教的悄然接管。然后自由派联合起来</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-15/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/a-tel-aviv-suburb-gave-in-to-a-creeping-orthodox-takeover-then-the-liberals-joined-forces/00000190-1994-d880-a7f5-bdd491810000</link><description>当中左翼联手建立统一战线来对抗城市的宗教政客时，会发生什么？一次特别甜蜜的选举胜利的故事</description><pubDate>Sat, 15 Jun 2024 03:10:32 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-15/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/a-tel-aviv-suburb-gave-in-to-a-creeping-orthodox-takeover-then-the-liberals-joined-forces/00000190-1994-d880-a7f5-bdd491810000</guid></item><item><title>以色列陷入战争，第 252 天：真主党向以色列北部发射数十枚火箭，毁坏房屋</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-14/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-252-hezbollah-fires-dozens-of-rockets-on-north-israel-damaging-homes/00000190-17a4-df11-a3b9-b7a7d79c0000</link><description>真主党向以色列北部发射数十枚火箭弹和无人机 ■ 哈马斯官员向 CNN 表示：“没有人知道”加沙地带还有多少人质 ■ 以色列官员：如果哈马斯不撤回改变，以色列将不会派代表团参加停火谈判拜登的提议 ■ 以色列士兵在约旦河西岸撞击事件中受伤 ■ 战争进入 252 天后，您需要了解以下内容</description><pubDate>Fri, 14 Jun 2024 17:09:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-14/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-252-hezbollah-fires-dozens-of-rockets-on-north-israel-damaging-homes/00000190-17a4-df11-a3b9-b7a7d79c0000</guid></item><item><title>连环犯罪分子统治着以色列。这就是崩溃开始的地方</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2024-06-14/ty-article-opinion/.premium/serial-criminals-rule-israel-thats-where-the-collapse-begins/00000190-1744-d4b4-a7d6-dff63e140000</link><description>以色列不再有真正的国家审计长、国家检察官、公务员委员会或司法部负责调查警察不当行为。内塔尼亚胡的影响力无处不在</description><pubDate>Fri, 14 Jun 2024 16:46:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2024-06-14/ty-article-opinion/.premium/serial-criminals-rule-israel-thats-where-the-collapse-begins/00000190-1744-d4b4-a7d6-dff63e140000</guid></item></channel></rss>